    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E92 M3 in collector-quality condition. This specimen features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power through eight individual throttle bodies to a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast shifts, while the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and M-Variable Differential Lock ensure surgical handling. This vehicle is mechanically flawless; proactive rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator services have been performed to ensure long-term reliability. The factory carbon fiber roof is pristine, showing no clear coat failure, and the chassis remains free of any oxidation or subframe fatigue. Inside, the Novillo leather retains its original matte finish with zero bolster wear. This is a turnkey, concours-level example for the discerning purist.",
