      "description": "This is a true showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior features its original factory paint, which has been treated with a multi-stage paint correction and a professional ceramic coating; there are absolutely no swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition, retaining that fresh leather scent with zero wear on the seat bolsters or steering wheel. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having followed a strict maintenance schedule exclusively at authorized dealerships\u2014full service records are organized and ready for your review. It sits on pristine alloy wheels wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread remaining. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that drives exactly as it did the day it left the lot.",
